====''Pokémon the Series''====
{{main|Lyra (anime)}}
Shortly after the release of {{game|HeartGold and SoulSilver|s}}, a counterpart of Lyra appeared in {{aniseries|DP}} from ''[[DP143|An Egg Scramble!]]'' to ''[[DP147|Bagged Then Tagged!]]''. Much as with {{an|May}}, {{an|Dawn}}, and {{an|Serena}}, she shares both her English and Japanese names with the player character she is based on. Along with her friend [[Khoury]], she traveled with {{Ash}} and {{ashfr}} for a short time, before ultimately returning to [[Johto]].
